          java.lang.String operation
          Has only setter to prevent setting the "operation" hidden field after executing the business logic. In this mode we avoid reexecuting the last business logic operation in case of a submit caused by changig the tab. The same effect can be achieved if we reset expicitely the "operation" field after executing the specific operation or if we do not use hidden field at all but only set the "operation" as request parameter
